window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Running a new Guild is no picnic, especially when you're the Chosen of the Black Dawn.</b></p> <p>Guilds everywhere want to snuff us out before we can even get off the ground, and enemies from outside of Millbank and even Earth are determined to take us down.</p> <p>It's a good thing there are expansion weapon cards that might just help us even the odds a little.</p>"; 
